?  I don't think black can chase down the white horse, or should waste time trying.  Though pushing it against the far right side of the board while the pawns are on the left may be a decent long term strategy.  Black's king is better off shepherding pawns, or gutting the king.  Pg blocks any further movement of the h pawn.  So Pf should be promoted.
